{"tid":2119722,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"精神病人睇完幻愛好大感觸","createTime":"2020-07-22T09:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T04:09:23.000Z","uid":200788,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cdbcd9bf3ee104b6a6ff3d00a83ccea3fa79c215","tid":2119722,"uid":200788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:00:33.000Z","msg":"好渴望愛情，想有人接納自己，但同時覺得自己唔可愛。<br />\n一諗起自己有咁多精神病，百病纏身咁就想摺埋，唔想害人。<br />\n<br />\n以前都會覺得自己BuildUp咗好多「可愛」嘅一面出嚟，討好到人就得。然而後尾發現親密嘅人唔會接受我發作嘅一面，例如話要我開心先肯陪住我，要我改好咗啲咩咩咩先理我。有時明明只係去搵自己嘅情緒同行為嘅原因，了解自己，但就俾朋友話我搵野去合理化自己行為。甚至喺背後嘲諷，厭倦我，令我好大打擊，更加覺得真正嘅自己係唔值得被愛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我可能要食成世藥，而且會復發。」<br />\n現實中又有幾多個葉嵐會唔介意？"},{"pid":"942083663363a2fad67d3de697cbc4637c6e3b50","tid":2119722,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"我唔介意"},{"pid":"c326d7b758d750b9b17ee6d2e3792bfb8f24d6e6","tid":2119722,"uid":34084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"有講長禁咩？"},{"pid":"cad5122f284ae0daf629cd8d4685646eb7898e83","tid":2119722,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:03:48.000Z","msg":"習慣孤獨是一件好事"},{"pid":"05cad4559dbf4e07f5e5df6b3c7703b1263db0cb","tid":2119722,"uid":179139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"有得食藥 有病徵咪算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4bb4bef82a3485051282c83ab5bd092cc6df57","tid":2119722,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:06:16.000Z","msg":"有時有啲關口可能都係要靠自己"},{"pid":"1ca09f236e058cccf3782629189a31dfad1ade54","tid":2119722,"uid":125898,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"069224cdf504aff412b58c4a1b0794fb7886bcc5","tid":2119722,"uid":278858,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cdbcd9bf3ee104b6a6ff3d00